      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Amend KRS 164.786 to include a proprietary school in the definition of \"participating institution\" for the purpose of the Dual Credit Scholarship Program; amend KRS 164.787 to include a proprietary school in the definition of \"eligible institution\" for the purpose of the Work Ready Kentucky Scholarship Program."
